ActTerritorial Lands Act
SubjectWithdrawal from Disposal of Certain Tracts of Territorial Lands in the Northwest Territories (Thaidene Nene (East Arm of Great Slave Lake) Naktional Park Reserve) Order
PrecisWITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN TRACTS OF TERRITORIAL LANDS IN THE THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES (THAIDENE NENE (EAST ARM OF GREAT SLAVE LAKE) NATIONAL PARK RESERVE) ORDER in order to (1) repeal the existing Withdrawal made by Order-in-Council P.C. 2012-409 of April 5, 2012; and (2) withdraw from disposal the surface and subsurface rights of certain lands (approximately 26,350 square kilometres) to facilitate the establishment of a national park in the Thaidene Nene (East Arm of Great Slave Lake) area in the Nortwest Territories.
RegistrationRegistration: SI/ 2014-0036 Publication Date: 2014-04-09
